{"word":"G541 - ἀπαύγασμα - apaúgasma - ap-ow'-gas-mah - Brightness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαύγασμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>apaúgasma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ap-ow'-gas-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Brightness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பிரகாசம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"reflected brightness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G826 - αὐγάζω - augázō - ow-gad'-zo/826\">G826</a>; an <i>off flash</i>, that is, <i>effulgence:</i> - brightness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G541 - ἀπαύγασμα - apaúgasma - ap-ow'-gas-mah/541\">G541</a>, <a href=\"#/G826 - αὐγάζω - augázō - ow-gad'-zo/826\">G826</a>"}]}